SIRV3   PacBio  exon    7271    7362    .   +   .   gene_id "PB.5"; transcript_id "PB.5.6";
SIRV3   PacBio  exon    7862    7988    .   +   .   gene_id "PB.5"; transcript_id "PB.5.6";
SIRV3   PacBio  exon    8125    8207    .   +   .   gene_id "PB.5"; transcript_id "PB.5.6";
SIRV3   PacBio  exon    8756    8935    .   +   .   gene_id "PB.5"; transcript_id "PB.5.6";
```

For **SIRV403**, the 3rd and 4th junction are different and shifted by 6 bp.

(in old, is correct)
```
SIRV4   PacBio  transcript  8324    15121   .   -   .   gene_id "PB.9"; transcript_id "PB.9.1";
SIRV4   PacBio  exon    8324    8372    .   -   .   gene_id "PB.9"; transcript_id "PB.9.1";
